parameters:
Hello. This is the Adventurer's Guild. Oh... are you a
student? I'm sorry, but part-time jobs are prohibited until
graduation. I apologize.

I sense the intention of strengthening the country's power
in recent requests.... Are they planning to start a war...?
No, it can't be...

Oh, are you students? There may come a time when I'll
request your help. I'll count on you then.

It's quite a burden for me with two warriors and only one
mage.... Maybe I should try recruiting someone nice....
The waiting time at the government office is so long...

Lately, there have been many people coming to the guild to
receive requests from outside. I have to work hard so that I
don't lose any jobs.

It's my first time coming to Caudine, but it seems stable.
It's also grateful that they hire outsiders like me.
